question: I am an agent and I registered as an Assister on Virginia's Insurance Marketplace now I cannot access my account.
text:
I am an agent and I registered as an Assister on Virginia's Insurance Marketplace now I cannot access my account.
          
        
If you completed the Assister registration by accident you will not be able to claim either account. You must call Virginia's Insurance Marketplace's dedicated agent and assister line for assistance at 1-888-687-1502.
